OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has agreed to foot the  
OL,6, bill for the compensation of former    
OL,7, Post Office workers who were falsely   
OL,8, convicted of theft in the long-running 
OL,9, Horizon saga.                          
OL,11,FThe Post Office has said they are      
OL,12,Funable to cover the payments for the   
OL,13,Fexonerated individuals.                
OL,15,FAs the Post Office's only shareholder, 
OL,16,Fthe government has now agreed to pay,  
OL,17,Fas first reported by Sky News.         
OL,19,FDetails are set to be announced in     
OL,20,FParliament as early as Tuesday.        
